HEADWORD: Jointweed
<hw>Joint"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A slender, nearly leafless, American herb (<spn>Polygonum
articulatum</spn>), with jointed spikes of small flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

